This is an introduction to UX
-> A User Experience designer as the name suggests focuses on how a user interacts with your product.
-> It is the job of a UX designer to make the product enjoyable, equitable, useful, and usable for the user.
-> A UX designer can either work with a big MNC, a startup or a design studio.
-> There various types of UX designers like, interactive, visual and many more.
-> They can be expert of one field or have a basic knowledge of all types and depth of knowledge on one of the types.
